      "starter_code": "# Dockerfile\n# 1. Start from Python 3.12 slim\n# 2. Set working directory to /app\n# 3. Copy requirements.txt and install\n# 4. Copy the rest of the code\n# 5. Expose port 5000\n# 6. CMD to run: python -m flask run --host=0.0.0.0",
